attributes.title: Nano Speed 9900 badminton racket
attributes.description:
Created on April 9, 2010 by dnghi1990 on Sourcemap.org:

This is one of the top models of badminton rackets available for now.It is often used by the professional players due to its advanced functionality and ease of use. Nevertheless, the material used in making this product is considered not eco-friendly at all.
